# TempTicket — Cursor rules

## Next.js

This repo may use Next.js APIs and structure that differ from older docs. Before changing routing, data fetching, or config, read the guides under `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` and respect deprecations.

## Stack (when relevant)

- Next.js (App Router), Tailwind, shadcn/ui.
- Auth/product patterns may use Postgres (e.g. Neon), Resend, magic-link / code flows — only what the codebase already uses.

## Product & UI

- Do not describe or expose environment variables or secrets in user-visible copy.
- For image and video uploads in product flows, use real upload-to-storage patterns — do not ship flows that only accept pasted URLs as the primary mechanism.

## Code changes

- Prefer small, focused diffs; match existing naming, imports, and component style in touched files.
- Run the project linter/build when changes are non-trivial.

## Workspace docs

- See `AGENTS.md` for the canonical Next.js reminder delegated from `CLAUDE.md`.

